<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109064>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Genus Otidiogryllacris: A–E, O. auriculata (Krauss, 1902) male (A–C) and female (D–E); F–J, O. lawang sp. nov. female holotype; K–O, O. bamusbama sp. nov. male holotype.—Habitus dorsal view (A, F, K), habitus lateral view (D, G), face (H, L), male abdominal apex in dorsal (B), oblique ventro-lateral (C), lateral (M), and ventral view (N), projections of ninth abdominal tergite in greater magnification (O); female end of abdomen with seventh sternite, subgenital plate and base of ovipositor in ventral (E, I) and lateral view (J). Scales 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109064/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

